        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Ancestral/scene_bulldog.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 6dfe141c-fa3b-422a-a28e-3ce2af1069ed).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening 47.\rThis contract has come in from a high-profile client, Alexa Carlisle. Ms. Carlisle has been alerted to some of her private staff having negotiations with press to reveal the faking of her death. She asks that you swiftly remove these staff members in tragic accidents before they can release the information. She will deposit a hefty bonus if the bodies are stashed for her &apos;cleaners&apos; to retrieve later.\rGood luck, 47. But I&apos;m sure you won&apos;t need it.",
